 *       - value              {string}
 *       - valueTo            {string}  Optional second value for between.
 *       - referenceTable     {string}  For reference type.
 *       - displayField       {string}  For reference type.
 *       - searchFields       {string}  For reference type.
 *       - referenceSearchField {string} Optional per-field override for reference text operators.
 *   @param  {number} page    - Current page number (1-based).
 *   @return {Array<Object>}  Array of plain objects. Each object must contain a key
 *                            per active column name plus the id field.
